JSON Serialization and Deserialization capabilities

Added `@jsonField` and `@jsonRequired` attributes to allow generating serialization / deserialization code for arbitrary types.

Serialization is implemented via `serializeJSON`. Deserialization is implemented via `deserializeJSON`.

Sample code:

---
struct SomeData
{
    @jsonField int a;
    @jsonField string b;
}

auto deserialized = deserializeJSON!SomeData(parseJSON(q{{"a": 12, "b": "test"}}));
---
